  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Single-level lumbar instrumented postero-lateral fusion from L2-L5

          -  Life expectancy greater than 2 years

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Previous lumbar surgery

          -  Spine tumour/cancer

          -  Documented osteoporosis

          -  High grade (3 or 4) spondylolisthesis
      </textblock>
